CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 18, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Will They Go? It is hoped that these lads will never go to war.  Eugene Stevens looks a little dubious at Clair Ford's 'jeep' at Francis Street and Wylie Avenue. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Boy wearing helmet and seated in toy tank, Francis Street at Wylie Avenue, Hill District
